-- Bear Stearns sees Q4 loss
-- 
-- Wed Nov 14, 2007 8:56am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/14/us-bearstearns-results-idUSWEN256420071114

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bear Stearns Cos Inc's BSC.N expected fourth-quarter write-down means the company will likely post a loss for the quarter, Chief Financial Officer Sam Molinaro said on Wednesday. 

 Speaking at a conference, CFO and Chief Operating Officer Molinaro said Bear Stearns has a strong balance sheet. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins  and  Joseph A. Giannone , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)